translate-toolkit (A toolkit to convert different translation formats)

The Translate Toolkit includes programs to covert localization formats
to the common PO,  and emerging XLIFF format.  There are also programs
to check and manage PO and XLIFF files.  Online documentation includes
guides on using the tools,  running a localization  project and how to
localize various projects from OpenOffice.org to Mozilla.

http://toolkit.translatehouse.org